Dear [Name],

I hope this finds you well and in good health.
My name is [Your Name], and I’m looking to buy your property at [Address].
I’m willing to pay you CASH and avoid the costs of selling through a real estate agent.

   *EASY to work with!
   *CASH BUYER
   *BUY AS-IS so no REPAIRS
   *CLOSE on the date of YOUR choice

Please call [Your Phone Number] today!

Smith Kermit R
2122 Riding Crop Way
Windsor Mill, MD 21244
